In each 10‑K, CVS presents a table of incurred and paid health‑care claims for the current year and the immediately preceding year as **unaudited supplemental information**.  
• The 2022 filing shows 2021 and 2020 data;  
• The 2023 filing shows 2022 and 2023 data;  
• The 2024 filing shows 2023 and 2024 data.  

The format—columns for incurred claims, paid claims, totals, outstanding liabilities, and a reconciliation to the health‑care costs payable liability—remains the same, with only the year labels and figures updated to reflect the most recent period.
